title: Urbanization in Chile 2018
yAxis: Share of urban population in total population
summary: In general Share of urban population in total population has stayed the same over the Year.
Share of urban population in total population is slightly increasing from 2008 to 2014.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2008 and 2009.
The highest Share of urban population in total population, of value 87.3 was reached at Year 2014
Minimum Share of urban population in total population about 86.96 was reached at Year 2008
